      "text": "2. In view of the fact/the observation of the flying saucers was made corresponds closely with the date of the unsigned telegram, and considering the proximity of [REDACTED] to the points where the objects were observed, it is requested that [REDACTED] be investigated to determine whether or not he has information pertaining to the origin of Flying Saucers.",
